#: ../maps/temple_of_mez_2.txt:555
msgid ""
"You cut into your arm with the Knife of Sacrifices. The pain is "
"excruciating. Shaking, you manage to collect some of your blood in a small "
"vial. The knife quickly raises in temperature until it disintegrates. Your "
"wound then begins to close itself, leaving no trace at all besides a warm "
"feeling throughout your body."
msgstr ""
"你用献祭之刃割破了你的手腕，痛苦的感觉如千刀万剐。在这时，你颤抖地把血装入瓶中。突然，献祭之刃升温炸裂，变成了碎片。不过，你的伤口逐渐恢复如初，只留下一股神秘的暖流涌遍全身。"

#: ../maps/temple_of_mez_2.txt:564
msgid "Red Altar"
msgstr "赤色祭坛"

