#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:1
msgid "Return to Empyrean"
msgstr "回到最高天"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:7
msgid ""
"You found a chamber on the east side of Perdition Harbor that contains the "
"Book of the Dead."
msgstr "你于避风港东侧的地下室找到了死亡之书。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:12
msgid ""
"The Book of the Dead states redemption is possible for those who sign their "
"name in gravebloom ink. Florin in Perdition Harbor can tell you more."
msgstr "死亡之书可以救赎签名于其上的人。你可以询问避风港里的弗洛里。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:17
msgid ""
"Before leaving St. Maria's Crypt, it would be wise to look for anything "
"useful."
msgstr "在离开圣玛利亚墓穴前，最好找一找有用之物。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:22
msgid "Ask Florin about the Gravebloom flower."
msgstr "向弗洛里询问坟墓之花。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:28
msgid ""
"You've found a gravebloom flower. It is a primary component in the creation "
"of gravebloom ink."
msgstr "你找到了坟墓之花。它是制作坟墓之墨的首要原料。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:33
msgid ""
"A strange black feather fell off of Mez. You should take it before leaving "
"the Temple of Mez."
msgstr "梅兹掉落了一个奇怪的黑色羽毛。你在离开神庙前最好带上。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:38
msgid "Ask Florin about the Black Quill."
msgstr "向弗洛里询问黑羽毛笔。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:44
msgid ""
"The Black Quill you found is the only thing capable of holding gravebloom "
"ink. It will be the only way to write in the Book of the Dead."
msgstr "你找到的黑色羽毛是唯一能够容纳坟墓之墨的东西。它是书写死亡之书的唯一方式。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:49
msgid ""
"Before leaving the Wizard's Tower, you should take the knife that Metzger "
"dropped."
msgstr "在离开巫师塔之前，你应该拿走梅茨格掉下的那把刀。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:54
msgid "Ask Florin about the Knife of Sacrifices."
msgstr "向弗洛里询问献祭之刃。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:60
msgid ""
"Gravebloom ink requires a sample of your blood to be drawn with the Knife of"
" Sacrifices. This must take place at the Red Altar in the Temple of Mez."
msgstr "制作坟墓之墨需要用献祭之刃割下你的血。你必须在梅兹神庙中的赤色祭坛做这件事。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:66
msgid ""
"Having completed the ritual at the Red Altar, return to Florin to proceed "
"with creating the gravebloom ink."
msgstr "在赤色祭坛收集完血后，回到弗洛里身旁。他会制作坟墓之墨。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:71
msgid ""
"The time has come. Write your name in the Book of the Dead and gain entry to"
" the Underworld."
msgstr "等待已久的时刻终于到了。在死亡之书上签名，然后去找地狱的入口。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:76
msgid ""
"Make your way to the Underworld. A portal to the Underworld was located in "
"the Wizard's Tower. Once you are there, search for a way to return to "
"Empyrean."
msgstr "前往地狱。通往地狱的传送门位于巫师塔中。到达那里后，寻找返回最高天的方法。"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:81
msgid ""
"You've found a stronghold in the Underworld. If there is a way back to "
"Empyrean, it is through here."
msgstr "你在地狱找到了一座要塞。从这里也许能返回最高天"

#: ../quests/0000_empyrean.txt:86
msgid "Face what awaits you in The Pit."
msgstr "在这地狱的尽头，请面对到来的一切。"

#: ../quests/0010_krolan.txt:1
msgid "Krolan's Missing"
msgstr "失踪的克罗兰"

#: ../quests/0010_krolan.txt:7
msgid "Travel to the Perdition Mines and look for Krolan."
msgstr "去毁灭之矿并找到克罗兰。"

#: ../quests/0010_krolan.txt:12
msgid "Use Krolan's key to search his chest."
msgstr "打开宝箱需要克罗兰的钥匙。"

#: ../quests/0010_krolan.txt:17
msgid "Return to Udana and inform her of Krolan's death."
msgstr "回到乌达娜身旁并告诉她克罗兰已经死了。"

#: ../quests/0011_alchemy.txt:1
msgid "Alchemy"
msgstr "炼金术"

#: ../quests/0011_alchemy.txt:7
msgid ""
"Florin requested a sample of 3 ingredients: Aloe Vera, Mana Crystals, and "
"Mushrooms."
msgstr "弗洛里需要各一份下列炼金用的原材料：精华草，灵能石和蘑菇。"

#: ../quests/0011_alchemy.txt:13
