msgstr "您捡到了一些蘑菇。"

#: ../quests/0011_alchemy.txt:31
msgid "You've found all 3 ingredients. Return them to Florin."
msgstr "你已经收集到了所有的炼金原料。将它们交给弗洛里。"

#: ../quests/0020_journal.txt:1
msgid "The Merchant's Journal"
msgstr "商人的日记"

#: ../quests/0020_journal.txt:8
msgid "Find Abasi's journal. It is likely being carried by a nearby goblin."
msgstr "找到阿巴斯的日记。它可能被附近的哥布林拿走了。"

#: ../quests/0020_journal.txt:14
msgid ""
"Find Abasi's journal. He said that it was last seen near the Goblin Cave."
msgstr "找到阿巴斯的日记。他说是在附近的哥布林洞穴最后一次看到日记。"

#: ../quests/0020_journal.txt:19
msgid "Return the journal to Abasi."
msgstr "把日记归还阿巴斯。"

#: ../quests/0030_ardwen.txt:1
msgid "Trapped in the Crypt"
msgstr "墓室惊魂"

#: ../quests/0030_ardwen.txt:6
msgid "Investigate the Family Crypt."
msgstr "调查家族墓地。"

#: ../quests/0030_ardwen.txt:10
msgid ""
"You found a strange ring. It might have a use beyond its mundane magical "
"properties."
msgstr "你找到了一个奇怪的戒指。它或许有着比强化自身属性更有趣的功能。"

#: ../quests/0030_ardwen.txt:14
msgid ""
"You found another strange ring. Maybe this one will have a different effect."
msgstr "您又找到了一个奇怪的戒指。或许它的效果和前一个不同。"

#: ../quests/0030_ardwen.txt:19
msgid "Defeat Ardwen."
msgstr "打倒艾德温。"

#: ../quests/0040_fort_amir.txt:1
msgid "The One-Eyed Guardians"
msgstr "独眼的守卫者"

#: ../quests/0040_fort_amir.txt:7
msgid "Investigate the statues in the Fort Amir throne room."
msgstr "调查阿米尔堡王座室里的雕像。"

#: ../quests/0040_fort_amir.txt:12
msgid "You found a strange sapphire inside one of Fort Amir's books."
msgstr "你在书里找到了一颗奇怪的宝石。"

#: ../quests/0040_fort_amir.txt:17
msgid "Gruzza dropped a strange sapphire."
msgstr "古扎掉落了一个奇怪的宝石。"

#: ../quests/0040_fort_amir.txt:22
msgid ""
"The bookcase in the Fort Amir throne room opened up, revealing a secret "
"passage."
msgstr "在阿米尔堡王座室中的一个书架忽然倒下了，露出了一个秘密通道。"

#: ../quests/0050_ort.txt:1
msgid "Brother?"
msgstr "兄弟？"

#: ../quests/0050_ort.txt:7
msgid ""
"Ort gave you a ruby. It seemed like he wanted it delivered to someone he "
"would call \"brother\"."
msgstr "奥特给了你一颗红宝石。他似乎想要把它交给某个他可以称为“弟弟”的人。"

#: ../quests/0060_stormrock.txt:1
msgid "Locked Out"
msgstr "锁上的门"

#: ../quests/0060_stormrock.txt:7
msgid ""
"The door to the Stormrock Ruins is locked. There must be a way to unlock it."
msgstr "暴雪遗迹的门被锁住了。一定有办法解锁它。"

#: ../quests/0060_stormrock.txt:12
msgid ""
"Aldwulf wants you to get the key to unlock the Stormrock Ruins. It should be"
" hidden somewhere in the camp south of Stonewood."
msgstr "阿尔德伍尔想让你拿到解锁暴雪遗迹的钥匙。它应该藏在石丛森林以南的营地某个地方。"

#: ../quests/0060_stormrock.txt:17
msgid ""
"You found the key to the Stormrock Ruins. You should return there and speak "
"to Aldwulf."
msgstr "你找到了暴雪遗迹的钥匙。你应该回去并与阿尔德伍尔交谈。"

#: ../quests/0070_nazia_mines.txt:1
msgid "The Buried Fortress"
msgstr "失落要塞"

#: ../quests/0070_nazia_mines.txt:7
msgid ""
"The excavation of the mines has revealed man-made structures. Perhaps this "
"is more than just a cave."
msgstr "矿井的挖掘揭示了人造结构。也许这不仅仅是一个洞穴。"

#: ../quests/0070_nazia_mines.txt:17
msgid ""
"You found a satchel of Blast Powder. Maybe an alchemist like Florin would "
"know how to make this into something more effective?"
msgstr "你发现了一袋爆炸粉。也许像弗洛里这样的炼金术士知道如何把它变成更有效的东西？"

#: ../quests/0070_nazia_mines.txt:22
msgid ""
"Mixing the Blast Powder with some shavings of a Mana Crystal has created "
"Dynamite. This could be useful."
msgstr "将爆炸粉与一些灵能石的碎屑混合，可以制造出炸药。这可能会很有用。"

#: ../quests/0070_nazia_mines.txt:27
msgid ""
"You successfully destroyed the previously barricaded door and can further "
"explore the Nazia Mines."
msgstr "你成功摧毁了先前被堵住的门，可以进一步探索纳吉矿洞。"

#: ../quests/0080_mog.txt:1
msgid "The Lost Soul of the Mog Caverns"
msgstr "洞中孤魂"

#: ../quests/0080_mog.txt:7
msgid ""
"You found a mysterious note in the Mog Caverns. Maybe its directions will "
"lead to treasure?"
msgstr "你在莫格洞穴中发现了一张神秘的纸条，也许它指引的方向会通往宝藏？"

#: ../quests/0080_mog.txt:17
msgid "A secret passage has been unveiled."
msgstr "你找到了一个秘密通道。"

#: ../quests/0090_nasu.txt:1
msgid "An Unusual Name..."
msgstr "一个古怪的名字..."

#: ../quests/0090_nasu.txt:7
msgid "Discover a way to open the entrance door in Fort Nasu."
msgstr "找到打开纳苏要塞入口大门的方法。"

#: ../quests/0090_nasu.txt:12
msgid "Discover a way to open the library door in Fort Nasu."
msgstr "找到打开纳苏要塞图书馆大门的方法。"

#: ../quests/0090_nasu.txt:17
msgid "Discover a way to open the pit room door in Fort Nasu."
msgstr "找到打开纳苏要塞地下室大门的方法。"

#: ../quests/0090_nasu.txt:22
msgid "Discover a way to open the final door in Fort Nasu."
msgstr "找到打开纳苏要塞最后一道大门的方法。"

#: ../quests/0090_nasu.txt:27
msgid "Defeat Buchi."
msgstr "打败布奇。"

#: ../quests/0100_torture.txt:1
msgid "Warden's Notes"
msgstr "狱长的笔记"

#: ../quests/0100_torture.txt:7
msgid "Find a way to get to the treasure in the Torture Chambers."
msgstr "找到前往折磨室中的宝藏的方法。"

#: ../quests/0100_torture.txt:12
msgid "You found some notes belonging to the prison warden."
msgstr "你找到了狱长的笔记。"

#: ../quests/0110_martigan.txt:1
msgid "Fallen Comrades"
msgstr "倒下的战友"

#: ../quests/0110_martigan.txt:7
msgid ""
"Martigan has asked you to destroy the undead corpses of his former "
"companions. He has also asked that you return with proof that you have done "
"so."
msgstr "马蒂根要求你摧毁他前战友的尸体。他还要求你带着完成此事的证据回来。"

#: ../quests/0110_martigan.txt:12
msgid "You have slain Lorund and recovered his sword."
msgstr "你杀死了洛伦德并取回了他的剑。"

#: ../quests/0110_martigan.txt:17
msgid "You have slain Nerin and recovered her bow."
msgstr "你杀死了内林并取回了她的弓。"

#: ../quests/0110_martigan.txt:22
msgid "You have slain Kayl and recovered her staff."
msgstr "你杀死了凯尔并取回了她的法杖。"

#: ../npcs/aldwulf.txt:1
msgid "Aldwulf, Treasure Hunter"
msgstr "阿尔德伍尔，宝藏猎人"

#: ../npcs/aldwulf.txt:10
msgid "Talk"
msgstr "谈话"

#: ../npcs/aldwulf.txt:12
msgid ""
"Greetings wanderer. I did not expect to meet anyone in a place like this."
msgstr "你好啊，远方的旅人。我没指望我能遇到任何人。"

#: ../npcs/aldwulf.txt:13
msgid ""
"I'm in a bit of a predicament. I wanted to come here in search of treasure, "
"but my partner disagreed with my intentions."
msgstr "我陷入了困境。我本来想来这里寻找宝藏的，但我的伙伴不同意我的想法。"

#: ../npcs/aldwulf.txt:14
msgid ""
"In an effort to stop me, he stole the key we found that supposedly opened "
"the door up ahead."
msgstr "为了阻止我，他偷走了我们找到的、据说能打开前门的那把钥匙。"

#: ../npcs/aldwulf.txt:15
msgid ""
"Regardless, I took my chances and left our camp south of Stonewood, hoping I"
" could break through without the key. As you might be able to tell, that "
"hasn't worked out in my favor."
msgstr "无论如何，我冒险离开了石丛森林以南的营地，希望我能在没有钥匙的情况下突破。正如你所见的，我失败了。"

#: ../npcs/aldwulf.txt:16
msgid ""
"If you come across my partner in your travels, do what you must to get that "
"key from him and bring it to me. Do that, and I'll split whatever we find in"
" these ruins with you."
msgstr "如果你在旅途中遇到我的伙伴，请用任何方法从他那里拿到那把钥匙并把它带给我。如果你这样做，我将与你分享我们在这些遗迹中发现的一切。"

#: ../npcs/aldwulf.txt:23
msgid ""
"Have you gotten the key yet? My partner likely has it hidden somewhere in "
"the camp south of Stonewood."
msgstr "你拿到钥匙了吗？我的伙伴可能把它藏在石丛森林以南的营地某个地方。"

#: ../npcs/ardwens_coffin.txt:12
msgid ""
"A finger-sized post is protruding from the lid of the coffin. It looks as "
"though something is missing."
msgstr "棺盖上有一个手指大小的柱子突出着。看起来好像缺少了什么。"

#: ../npcs/ardwens_coffin.txt:17
msgid "Place the Gold Family Ring on the coffin"
msgstr "将金色家族戒指放在棺材上"

#: ../npcs/ardwens_coffin.txt:22
msgid "The ring dissolved into nothing!"
msgstr "戒指化为虚无！"

#: ../npcs/ardwens_coffin.txt:30
msgid "Place the Silver Family Ring on the coffin"
msgstr "将银色家族戒指放在棺材上"

#: ../npcs/ardwens_coffin.txt:42
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

#: ../npcs/bakat.txt:1
msgid "Bakat, Goblin Packrat"
msgstr "巴卡，哥布林商人"

#: ../npcs/bakat.txt:20
msgid "Goblin's Ruby"
msgstr "哥布林的红宝石"

#: ../npcs/bakat.txt:24
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#: ../npcs/bakat.txt:31
msgid "(You show Bakat the ruby you received from Ort.)"
msgstr "（你将奥特给你的红宝石交给了巴卡。）"

#: ../npcs/bakat.txt:32
msgid "(Bakat snatches the jewel from your grasp.)"
msgstr "（激动的巴卡一把抓起你手中的宝石。）"

#: ../npcs/bakat.txt:33
msgid "(He holds the ruby up into the light and examines it closely.)"
msgstr "（他将红宝石举到光下，仔细检查。）"

#: ../npcs/bakat.txt:34
msgid ""
"(Looking satisfied, he reaches into his bag and hands you a wooden bear "
"figurine.)"
msgstr "（他满意地看着，并从袋子里拿出一个木制熊摆件递给你。）"

#: ../npcs/base/infinity_obelisk.txt:1
msgid "Infinity Obelisk"
msgstr "无尽方尖碑"

#: ../npcs/base/infinity_obelisk.txt:8
msgid "(You touch the obelisk, but nothing happens.)"
msgstr "（你伸手去摸方尖碑，不过什么都没发生。）"

#: ../npcs/base/infinity_obelisk.txt:11
msgid "Continue through the Halls of Infinity"
msgstr "继续冒险"

#: ../npcs/base/infinity_obelisk.txt:18
msgid "Return to Underworld Stronghold"
msgstr "回到地狱"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/common.txt:1
msgid "Abasi, Traveling Merchant"
msgstr "阿巴斯，旅行商人"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_common.txt:2
msgid "Journal"
msgstr "日记。"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_common.txt:5
msgid "Any luck finding my journal?"
msgstr "找到我的日记没？"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_common.txt:6
msgid "Not yet."
msgstr "暂时没有。"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_common.txt:13
msgid "Here is your journal."
msgstr "拿着，你的日记。"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_common.txt:14
msgid "Wonderful! I had considered it forever lost at this point."
msgstr "太赞了！我还以为我再也找不到它了。"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_common.txt:15
msgid "I am in your debt. Please take this as a reward for your trouble."
msgstr "我欠你个人情。作为回报，请收下我的小小心意。"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_common.txt:27
msgid "Show no mercy for those thieving goblins."
msgstr "不要怜悯那些哥布林窃贼。"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_intro1.txt:5
msgid "Be careful on these roads. Those goblins are nothing but trouble."
msgstr "在路上要当心。那些哥布林是个麻烦。"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_intro1.txt:6
msgid "Thanks for the warning."
msgstr "感谢你的提示。"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_intro1.txt:7
msgid "It's the least I can do."
msgstr "这是我能做的。"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_intro1.txt:8
msgid ""
"When I awoke this morning, my journal was missing. No doubt one of those "
"filthy green creatures stole it from me."
msgstr "当我今早醒来时，我的日记不见了。毫无疑问，肯定是那些肮脏的绿皮生物偷走了它。"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_intro1.txt:9
msgid "If you come across my journal in your travels, please return it to me."
msgstr "如果你在旅途中发现了我的日记，请把它交还给我。"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_intro2.txt:5
msgid "Greetings, wanderer."
msgstr "你好，远方的旅客。"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_intro2.txt:6
msgid ""
"Judging from your appearance, you're no stranger to a long journey. For that"
" reason, I ask that you keep an eye out for my missing journal."
msgstr "从你的外表来看，你对长途旅行并不陌生。因此，我请求你留意我丢失的日记。"

#: ../npcs/base/abasi/quest_intro2.txt:7
msgid ""
"I first noticed it was missing after a night of camping near the Goblin "
"Cave. I searched for a while, but ultimately decided it was best to move on."
msgstr "我是在哥布林洞穴附近露营一晚后才注意到它不见了。我找了一会儿，但最终还是决定离开。"

