#: ../npcs/florin.txt:1
msgid "Florin, Apothecary"
msgstr "药剂师弗洛里"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:27
msgid "What can you tell me about the Book of the Dead?"
msgstr "你能告诉我什么是死亡之书吗？"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:28
msgid ""
"The Book of the Dead tells of redemption for those who sign their name in "
"gravebloom ink. Your sins will be washed away, and you will be able to "
"return to wherever you were banished from."
msgstr "《死亡之书》会使那些用坟墓之墨签上自己名字的人获得救赎。你的罪恶必被洗去，你也必能回到你被赶出的地方。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:29
msgid "So, where can I find gravebloom ink?"
msgstr "所以哪里去找坟墓之墨？"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:30
msgid ""
"Gravebloom ink is not something you find. You must make it yourself. Besides"
" the Gravebloom flower, you will need to sacrifice your own blood with a "
"special blade."
msgstr "若想得到坟墓之墨，你不能守株待兔，你需要自己获得原料并制作它。除了坟墓之花，你还要用特殊的小刀来献祭自己的血。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:31
msgid ""
"Even if you can create some gravebloom ink, you won't be able to write with "
"just anything. The ink won't stick to a normal quill. You will need to find "
"something capable of holding the gravebloom ink."
msgstr "即使你能制作一些坟墓之墨，你也不能用任何东西来书写。墨水不会粘在普通的羽毛笔上。你需要找到某种能够容纳坟墓之墨的东西。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:32
msgid ""
"If you can perform the ritual to make gravebloom ink and find a suitable "
"writing utensil, redemption may be yours."
msgstr "如果你能完成制作坟墓之墨的仪式并找到合适的书写工具，你将获得救赎。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:35
msgid "Gravebloom"
msgstr "坟墓之花"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:39
msgid ""
"Ah yes, that is most certainly a gravebloom flower. It is the primary "
"component in the creation of gravebloom ink."
msgstr "啊，是的，那无疑是一朵坟墓之花。它是制作坟墓之墨的主要成分。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:42
msgid "Black Quill"
msgstr "黑羽毛笔"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:45
msgid "Do you think this quill is capable of holding gravebloom ink?"
msgstr "你认为这支羽毛笔能够容纳坟墓之墨吗？"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:46
msgid "It's certainly no normal quill. I've never seen anything like it."
msgstr "这绝对不是普通的羽毛笔。我从未见过这样的东西。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:48
msgid ""
"If anything is capable of writing with gravebloom ink, it is that quill."
msgstr "如果有什么东西能够用坟墓之墨书写，那就是这支羽毛笔。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:51
msgid "Knife of Sacrifices"
msgstr "献祭之刃"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:54
msgid "Do you know anything about this knife?"
msgstr "对这把刀你都知道些什么？"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:56
msgid ""
"The Knife of Sacrifices. This must be the blade you will need to draw your "
"blood for the gravebloom ink. From what I've read, this must be done at the "
"\"Red Altar\"."
msgstr "献祭之刃。你需要用它抽取你的‘血液’来制作坟墓之墨。根据我所读到的，这必须在“赤色祭坛”进行。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:57
msgid "I recall such an altar from the Temple of Mez."
msgstr "我记得在梅兹神庙里有这样一个祭坛。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:58
msgid ""
"I don't know why this blade in particular is required to make the ink. Once "
"it pierces your skin, there is no telling what effect it will have on you. "
"Please keep this in mind."
msgstr "我不知道为什么要用这把刀来制作特别的墨水。一旦它刺穿你的皮肤，你无法预知它会对你产生什么影响。请记住这一点。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:61
msgid "Vial of Blood"
msgstr "血瓶"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:66
msgid "I completed the ritual at the Red Altar. What now?"
msgstr "我在赤色祭坛完成了仪式。接下来呢？"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:67
msgid ""
"I can create a small amount of gravebloom ink for you, but I require a "
"Gravebloom flower accomplish this. Return to me with both the flower and the"
" blood."
msgstr "我可以为你制作少量坟墓之墨，但我需要一朵坟墓之花来完成。请带着花和血液回到我这里。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:75
msgid ""
"We are ready to create a small amount of gravebloom ink. Allow me to perform"
" the mixing."
msgstr "我们准备好制作少量坟墓之墨了。让我来混合一下吧。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:76
msgid ""
"The correct ratio of Gravebloom to blood is important. Too much Gravebloom "
"will cause the ink to eat through the paper. Too little Gravebloom and the "
"ink won't adhere to the quill."
msgstr "坟墓之花和血液的比例很重要。坟墓之花太多会导致墨水渗入纸张。坟墓之花太少，墨水将无法粘在羽毛笔上。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:77
msgid ""
"(Florin carefully mixes the two elements into a small inkwell, alternating "
"the additions of Gravebloom and blood.)"
msgstr "（弗洛里小心地将两种元素混合到一个小墨水瓶中，交替添加坟墓之花和血液。）"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:82
msgid ""
"Finished! I don't want my work to go to waste, so move now to the Book of "
"the Dead chamber."
msgstr "完成了！我不想让我的工作白费，所以现在就去死亡之书的房间吧。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:88
msgid "The ritual is complete. The Underworld is open to you."
msgstr "仪式完成了。地狱之门将为你敞开。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:89
msgid ""
"There was a portal to the Underworld in the Wizard's Tower. I shall return "
"there."
msgstr "巫师塔里有一个通往地狱的传送门。我将回到那里。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:94
msgid ""
"If you plan on venturing further, you'll need to learn how to use the "
"resources that you come across."
msgstr "如果你打算进一步冒险，你需要学会如何使用你获得的资源。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:95
msgid ""
"I can show you how to mix potions, but I don't have any ingredients on hand."
msgstr "我可以教你如何混合药剂，但我手边没有材料。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:96
msgid ""
"Can I ask you to procure some elements for me? I require one each of the "
"following: Aloe Vera, Mana Crystal, and Mushrooms."
msgstr "你能帮我采集一些炼金材料么？我需要精华草，灵能石和蘑菇各一份。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:97
msgid "I can do that."
msgstr "我可以这样做。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:99
msgid ""
"Then return to me with these items, and I will make it worth your time."
msgstr "那么带着这些物品回到我这里，我会让你物有所值。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:107
msgid "Have you gotten those ingredients yet?"
msgstr "你已经弄到那些材料了吗？"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:112
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:119
msgid "Here are the ingredients you asked for."
msgstr "这是你要求的材料。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:120
msgid ""
"Thank you. I was able to find some Aloe Vera on my own, so you can keep what"
" you found."
msgstr "多谢。我已经自己采集到了一些精华草，这些精华草你就自己留着吧。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:121
msgid ""
"Also, take these empty bottles along with this mortar and pestle. You can "
"use the mortar and pestle with that Aloe Vera you found to make a fine "
"healing potion."
msgstr "还有，这些空瓶子和这对杵臼你也带上吧。你可以用杵臼捣碎野外采集到的精华草，从而做出来一份上好的治疗药剂。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:122
msgid ""
"If you ever lose that mortar and pestle, you can always speak to me if you "
"want some potions made."
msgstr "如果你想做药剂时却发现自己不小心把杵臼弄丢了，尽管来向我要。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:127
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:137
msgid "Blast Powder"
msgstr "火药粉末"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:139
msgid ""
"Blast powder? With a little bit of Mana Crystal, you can make quite the "
"explosion with that stuff."
msgstr "火药粉末？只要你加一点点灵能石，就可以利用它制造一场大爆炸。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:140
msgid "The process is fairly volatile, so allow me to do the mixing."
msgstr "这个过程相当不稳定，所以让我来混合一下。"

#: ../npcs/florin.txt:147
msgid "There. Now be careful with that."
msgstr "就是这样。现在要小心使用它。"

#: ../npcs/glowing_obelisk_1.txt:1
msgid "Glowing Obelisk"
msgstr "发光方尖碑"

#: ../npcs/iron_labyrinth_teleporter.txt:1
msgid "Strange Obelisk"
msgstr "奇怪的方尖碑"

#: ../npcs/iron_labyrinth_teleporter.txt:21
msgid "Choose a destination."
msgstr "选择一个目的地。"

#: ../npcs/loren.txt:1
msgid "Loren, Undead Trader"
msgstr "老任，亡灵商人"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:1
msgid "Martigan"
msgstr "马蒂根"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:19
msgid ""
"You there! I need your help. I'm the last of my group, and want nothing more"
" than to leave this place."
msgstr "你在那里！我需要你的帮助。我是我队伍的最后一人，只想离开这里。"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:20
msgid ""
"Yet I have one remaining task. I wish to visit the graves of my three fallen"
" partners one last time."
msgstr "但我还有一个任务。我想最后一次拜访我三位倒下的伙伴的坟墓。"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:21
msgid ""
"To my disadvantage, their bodies have been taken by the soil here. They "
"tried to attack me when I got near."
msgstr "对我来说不利的是，他们的尸体已经被这里的土壤吞噬了。当我靠近时，他们试图攻击我。"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:22
msgid ""
"If you can prove to me that they are free from their cursed form, I will be "
"in your debt."
msgstr "如果你能证明他们已经摆脱了诅咒的形态，我将欠你一份人情。"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:23
msgid "I can't assist you myself, but I can offer some of my wares."
msgstr "我不能亲自帮你，但我可以提供一些我的货物。"

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:29
msgid "Zombies"
msgstr "僵尸 "

#: ../npcs/martigan.txt:39
msgid ""
"Indeed, these items belonged to my companions. I want you to take this as a "
"reward."
msgstr "确实，这些物品属于我的伙伴们。我希望你把这些当作一份奖励。"

#: ../npcs/ort.txt:1
msgid "Ort, Goblin Packrat"
msgstr "奥特，哥布林商人"

#: ../npcs/ort.txt:29
msgid "... Bro-ther... g-give..."
msgstr "……给我的……弟弟……"

#: ../npcs/ort.txt:30
msgid "(Ort grabs your hand and places a red gem in it.)"
msgstr "（奥特紧握着你的手，并塞给了你一个红色的宝石。）"

#: ../npcs/tutorial.txt:1
msgid "Skeleton with note"
msgstr "带信的骸骨"

#: ../npcs/tutorial.txt:9
msgid "Tutorial"
msgstr "教程"

#: ../npcs/tutorial.txt:11
msgid ""
"Welcome to the lands of the exiled. Allow me to go over a few things. Click "
"on the arrow to continue."
msgstr "欢迎来到放逐之地。请允许我逐项介绍。点击箭头以继续。"

#: ../npcs/tutorial.txt:12
msgid ""
"Your health, mana, and experience points are displayed in the top left of "
"the screen."
msgstr "你的生命值、魔力值、经验点数如屏幕左上方所示。"

#: ../npcs/tutorial.txt:13
msgid "In the top right is a map of your current location."
msgstr "右上方是你所在位置的小型地图。"

#: ../npcs/tutorial.txt:14
msgid ""
"On the bottom of the screen is your action bar. Here, you have quick access "
"to your most used abilities."
msgstr "屏幕下方是快捷操作栏。你可以在这里快速操作常用功能。"

#: ../npcs/tutorial.txt:15
msgid ""
"In addition, you can access the Character, Inventory, Powers, and Log menus "
"from the action bar."
msgstr "你也可以直接在快捷操作栏上访问角色、物品、力量、日志菜单。"

#: ../npcs/tutorial.txt:16
msgid ""
"${INPUT_MOVEMENT} will allow you to move around. ${INPUT_ATTACK} will use "
"your primary attack."
msgstr "${INPUT_MOVEMENT}允许你四处移动. ${INPUT_ATTACK} 将发动主要攻击动作."

#: ../npcs/tutorial.txt:17
msgid "Good luck!"
msgstr "祝你好运！"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:1
msgid "Udana, Metalworker"
msgstr "铁匠乌达娜"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:30
msgid ""
"Greetings stranger. It's not often that we have people come here from the "
"west."
msgstr "你好，外乡人。我们这儿很少碰见西方的来客。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:31
msgid ""
"I see that you're carrying a weapon. Would you be interested in helping us?"
msgstr "我看到你配有武器。你有兴趣帮我们个忙吗？"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:32
msgid "Go on."
msgstr "但说无妨。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:33
msgid ""
"One of our encampment's residents, Krolan, works in the nearby mines. He "
"supplies me with various gems that I craft into jewelery."
msgstr "我们营地的居民克罗兰在附近的矿场工作。他为我提供了各种宝石，而我将其制作成珠宝。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:34
msgid ""
"Krolan has not returned in some time, and I am starting to think the worst."
msgstr "克罗兰有段时间没回来了，也许他遇到了什么麻烦。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:35
msgid ""
"Could you please travel to the mines and look for Krolan? I will find some "
"way to reward you for your trouble."
msgstr "你可以去矿场寻找克罗兰吗？我会想办法答谢你的。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:44
msgid ""
"Please hurry to find Krolan. The Perdition Mines are located near the Salted"
" Field."
msgstr "希望可以尽早找到克罗兰，毁灭之矿就在盐碱之地的附近。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:60
msgid "I have found Krolan, but he was no longer of this world."
msgstr "我找到克罗兰了，可惜他已与世长辞。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:61
msgid ""
"This is terrible news. Our camp is already small, so this is a devastating "
"loss."
msgstr "糟透了，我们的营地本来就小，对我们而言，失去他几乎要毁了这里。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:62
msgid ""
"If it's any solace, I have his key and this emerald. Mementos to remember "
"him by."
msgstr "所幸我还留有他的钥匙和这块翡翠石，希望可以在纪念他时聊以慰藉。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:63
msgid ""
"The key is enough of a memento. For your invaluable help, I can at least "
"make you a ring with this emerald."
msgstr "就纪念亡者来说，钥匙差不多够了。作为你的报酬，我至少可以用这块翡翠石为你打造一枚指环。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:77
msgid "Can you tell me about the nearby cave?"
msgstr "你能告诉我关于附近的洞穴的事情吗？"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:78
msgid "It was a mining operation. Krolan was a part of the crew."
msgstr "那是一个采矿作业。克罗兰是那支队伍的一员。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:79
msgid ""
"Not long into their dig, they encountered ruins. Ruins unlike any of the "
"structures in this region."
msgstr "他们挖掘没多久就发现了遗迹。这些遗迹与这个地区任何结构都不同。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:80
msgid ""
"Amongst these ruins, the crew found an incredible glowing mineral: Mastite."
msgstr "在这些遗迹中，队伍发现了一种令人难以置信的发光矿物：魔石。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:81
msgid ""
"When the Empyrean caught wind of this discovery, they promptly took control "
"of the operation."
msgstr "当最高天得知这一发现后，他们立即接管了这项作业。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:82
msgid "So why is it blocked off now? Did the Empyrean strip it clean?"
msgstr "那么为什么现在被封锁了？最高天是不是把它们全部清空了？"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:83
msgid ""
"The further the excavation team dug, the more apparent it became that "
"something was unusual about the ruins. North would become south, west would "
"become east. They were losing workers."
msgstr "挖掘队越深入，就越显示这些遗迹有些不寻常。北方变成了南方，西方变成了东方。他们正在失去工人。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:84
msgid ""
"The Empyrean shut down the operation. Instead, they made an effort to mine "
"other nearby areas in hope of finding a more stable source of Mastite. "
"You've already seen the futile end to that story."
msgstr "最高天关闭了这项作业。相反，他们努力在附近的其他区域开采，希望能找到更稳定的魔石来源。你已经看到了这个故事的徒劳结局。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:85
msgid ""
"If the Empyrean gave up on the ruins, there may still be some value in "
"exploring it. Is there any way I can get inside?"
msgstr "如果最高天放弃了这些遗迹，探索它们可能仍然有价值。我有进去的办法吗？"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:86
msgid ""
"It's risky, but you proven that you're able to handle yourself. And maybe if"
" we can gain our own supply of Mastite, we'll have some leverage against the"
" Empyrean."
msgstr "这很危险，但你证明了你能自保。如果我们能获得自己的魔石供应，我们也许就能对最高天增加一些筹码。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:87
msgid ""
"Here. I made a copy of the key you'll need after one of the Empyrean guards "
"dropped it. Please be careful. I'm not sure I'm ready to be exposed to any "
"more death."
msgstr "给你。在一位最高天卫兵掉落钥匙后，我做了一份副本。请小心，我不确定我是否准备好面对更多的死亡。"

#: ../npcs/udana.txt:104
msgid "Thank you again for your help."
msgstr "再次感谢你的帮助。"

#: ../npcs/yora.txt:1
msgid "Yora, Enchanter"
msgstr "巫师尤拉"

#: ../cutscenes/backstory.txt:8
msgid ""
"Empyrean, the city in the sky. It is a majestic fortress and the last "
"bastion of humankind."
msgstr "最高天，天空之城，雄伟的要塞，人类最后的堡垒。"

#: ../cutscenes/backstory.txt:10
msgid ""
"At the height of the kingdom's power the city was a beacon of peace and law."
msgstr "在王国的鼎盛时期，它是和谐与法治的标志。"

#: ../cutscenes/backstory.txt:12
msgid ""
"When darkness invaded the world in the last age people abandoned the "
"surface. Empyrean was their only refuge."
msgstr "黑暗侵袭，末世到来，人类逃离地表。最高天是他们最后的避难所。"

#: ../cutscenes/backstory.txt:14
msgid ""
"Now the Age of Humanity is ending. Empyrean is crumbling. Scarcity and "
"political infighting have consumed the city."
msgstr "如今，人类的时代快要落幕，最高天将要崩塌。物资匮乏与政府内讧快要吞噬这座城市了。"

#: ../cutscenes/backstory.txt:17
msgid ""
"Some, in desperation, flee to the surface hoping to survive without the "
"protection of the city."
msgstr "走投无路之时，有人弃城偷生，仓惶逃往地面。"

#: ../cutscenes/backstory.txt:19
msgid ""
"But no one returns from the surface. Most die or go missing. A few hide and "
"survive, for a while."
msgstr "然而，从未有人从地面安然归来。不是死亡就是失踪，还有些人暂时匿踪，苟且一时。"

#: ../cutscenes/backstory.txt:21
msgid ""
"Surface dwellers cling to hope. Hope that they'll return to Empyrean some "
"day. Hope that a hero will fight back against the darkness."
msgstr "地上的居民坚信，他们有朝一日可以重返最高天。未来会有英雄反击黑暗。"

#: ../cutscenes/backstory.txt:23
msgid ""
"There is always hope. But not for everyone: not for you. Not for the Exiled."
msgstr "世间希望尚存，并非凡人所有：不属于你，也不属于这些流放之人。"

#: ../cutscenes/credits_empyrean.txt:5
msgid "Flare Game Credits - empyrean_campaign"
msgstr "Flare Game 制作名单 - 最高天战役"

#: ../cutscenes/credits_empyrean.txt:8
msgid "Lead Content Designers"
msgstr "首席内容设计师"

#: ../cutscenes/credits_empyrean.txt:14
msgid "Visual Artists"
msgstr "画师"

#: ../cutscenes/credits_empyrean.txt:25
msgid "Foley Artists"
msgstr "音效师"

#: ../cutscenes/credits_empyrean.txt:31
msgid "Translators"
msgstr "译者"

#: ../cutscenes/ending.txt:8
msgid ""
"At long last, your journey across the surface and into the Underworld has "
"come to an end."
msgstr "终于，你穿越地表进入地狱的旅途结束了。"

#: ../cutscenes/ending.txt:10
msgid "Upon entering The Pit, a glowing obelisk shined in the distance."
msgstr "进入深渊时，一座发光的方尖碑在远处闪耀着光芒。"

#: ../cutscenes/ending.txt:12
msgid ""
"Guarding the obelisk was Lezaith, a formidable opponent, yet no match for "
"Exiled who faced her."
msgstr "守护着方尖碑的是莱扎伊，一个强大的对手，但她无法匹敌那些面对她的流放者。"

#: ../cutscenes/ending.txt:14
msgid "With Lezaith's defeat, the path to the obelisk was clear."
msgstr "随着莱扎伊的战败，通往方尖碑的道路变得清晰。"

#: ../cutscenes/ending.txt:17
msgid ""
"Not a moment after Lezaith crumbles into a pile of bones, a bolt of "
"lightning strikes the obelisk."
msgstr "莱扎伊化为一堆骨头后不到一刻，一道闪电击中了方尖碑。"

#: ../cutscenes/ending.txt:19
msgid ""
"Did Lezaith cast a spell on the obelisk with her dying breath? Had Empyrean "
"finally collapsed?"
msgstr "莱扎伊用最后的呼吸施放了魔法吗？最高天终于崩溃了吗？"

#: ../cutscenes/ending.txt:22
msgid ""
"Maybe it's true what they say. No one returns from the surface. Most die or "
"go missing. A few hide and survive, for a while."
msgstr "也许他们所说的是真的。从未有人从地面归来。不是死亡就是失踪，还有些人暂时匿踪，苟且一时。"

#: ../cutscenes/ending.txt:24
msgid "Even the Exiled."
msgstr "就连流放者也是如此。"

#: ../cutscenes/ending.txt:30
msgid "And a very special thanks to..."
msgstr "特别地，我们还有一位要感谢的人——"

#: ../cutscenes/ending.txt:31
msgid "You!"
msgstr "你自己！"

#: ../cutscenes/ending.txt:35
msgid "The End"
msgstr "结局"

#: ../books/book_of_the_dead.txt:13
msgid ""
"Those whose names are written here in gravebloom ink are admitted passage to"
" the trail of redemption."
msgstr "若想洗清罪恶，并回到你被放逐的地方，就用坟墓之墨，在这死亡之书上签下你的名字，获得救赎吧！"

