#: ../books/il_notes_1.txt:13
msgid "1462/3/10"
msgstr "1462/3/10"

#: ../books/il_notes_1.txt:19
msgid ""
"The dig near Perdition Harbor is starting to show promise. We found ruins. "
"Unlike anything else in the area. We'll get a good amount of gold from the "
"relics here. A welcome change for the guys that transferred from the "
"Empyrean's operation in the complex under Lochport."
msgstr ""
"在避风港附近的挖掘工作开始显示出希望。我们发现了遗迹。它们与该地区任何其他地方都不同。我们从这里的遗物中能获得大量的黄金。这对那些从隆港复杂的最高天业务转来的家伙来说，是一个受欢迎的转变。"

#: ../books/il_notes_1.txt:25
msgid "[Missing page]"
msgstr "[缺失页]"

#: ../books/il_notes_1.txt:32
msgid ""
"They told me about the other expeditions, a tower in Black Oak City and a "
"temple in the Stormrock region. Both just as fruitless."
msgstr "他们告诉我关于其他探险，黑橡镇的一座塔和一个暴雪区域的寺庙。两者都一样无望。"

#: ../books/il_notes_2.txt:13
msgid "1462/3/15"
msgstr "1462/3/15"

#: ../books/il_notes_2.txt:19
msgid ""
"Today, we found a peculiar yellow-green mineral. Almost blinding to look at."
" Perhaps someone from the Empyrean Chamber knows what it is..."
msgstr "今天，我们发现了一种奇特的黄绿色矿物。看起来几乎令人目眩。也许最高天议会的人知道它是什么……"

#: ../books/il_notes_2.txt:32
msgid "1462/3/16"
msgstr "1462/3/16"

#: ../books/il_notes_2.txt:38
msgid ""
"The messenger to the Chamber called the mineral \"Mastite\". It was made "
"clear that any we find must be brought to the surface. No questions. This "
"stuff is obviously something special. They better make it worth our while."
msgstr ""
"向议会的信使称这种矿物为“魔石”。他们明确表示，我们发现的任何东西都必须带到地表上来。毫无疑问，这些东西显然是特别的。他们最好让它值得我们付出努力"

#: ../books/il_notes_3.txt:13
msgid "1462/3/23"
msgstr "1462/3/23"

#: ../books/il_notes_3.txt:19
msgid ""
"There's more to this whole Mastite thing than we're being told. Yesterday, "
"one of the crew was about to grab a chunk he had found. In the blink of an "
"eye, some sort of energy ball flew out of it and blasted the poor guy back "
"about 100 paces."
msgstr ""
"关于这种魔石的事情，我们被告知的只是冰山一角。昨天，其中一名队员正准备拿走他发现的一块矿石。转瞬之间，某种能量球从它身上飞出，将那可怜的家伙击退了大约一百步。"

#: ../books/il_notes_3.txt:38
msgid ""
"What does the Chamber's healer do? Gives him a measly potion! Why are we "
"waiting until the damage is done? We need defensive mages! But somehow, "
"that's out of the question for the Empyrean..."
msgstr "议会的治疗师做了什么？只给了一个可怜的药水！我们为什么要等到伤害发生之后才行动？我们需要防御法师！但不知何故，这对最高天来说是不可能的……"

#: ../books/il_notes_4.txt:13
msgid "1462/3/25"
msgstr "1462/3/25"

#: ../books/il_notes_4.txt:19
msgid ""
"I've calmed down enough to write a coherent letter to the Chamber requesting"
" the resources we need. Now we just have to wait. In the meantime, we'll "
"continue exploring as carefully as possible."
msgstr "我已经冷静下来了，并写了一封有条理的信给议会，请求我们需要的资源。现在我们只能等待。在此期间，我们将尽可能小心地继续探索。"

#: ../books/il_notes_4.txt:32
msgid "1462/4/27"
msgstr "1462/4/27"

#: ../books/il_notes_4.txt:38
msgid ""
"The Chamber finally gave their response. They did send a few mages, but not "
"nearly enough. There's a promise of a larger gold share when the excavation "
"is complete. Somehow, I don't think Empyrean politics will allow such a "
"thing to manifest."
msgstr ""
"议会终于给出了回应。他们确实派了一些法师，但远远不够。挖掘完成后，会有一个更大的黄金份额的承诺。不知怎么的，我不认为最高天的政治会允许这种事情发生。"

#: ../books/il_notes_5.txt:13
msgid "1462/6/3"
msgstr "1462/6/3"

#: ../books/il_notes_5.txt:19
msgid ""
"These ruins are larger than we had imagined. There must be other connections"
" to the surface. Krolan found a portal today, but no one dared to enter."
msgstr "这些遗迹比我们想象的要大。地表上一定还有其他联系。克罗兰今天发现了一个传送门，但没有人敢进去。"

#: ../books/il_notes_5.txt:38
msgid ""
"We asked the mages to try analyzing it. Unfortunately, they reported not "
"being able to see through to the other side."
msgstr "我们请法师尝试分析它。不幸的是，他们报告说无法看到另一边。"

#: ../books/il_notes_6.txt:13
msgid "1462/8/12"
msgstr "1462/8/12"

#: ../books/il_notes_6.txt:19
msgid ""
"It's finally over! We reached a massive chamber inhabited by a giant "
"antlion! The mages were able to hold it back while we grabbed everything "
"that wasn't nailed down. Thought we were trapped when we had to barricade "
"the gate. Thank the heavens that the portal brought us back here."
msgstr ""
"终于结束了！我们到达了一个被巨型蚁狮占据的巨大房间！法师们在我们抢走所有固定住的东西时，成功地将它拦住了。当我们不得不堵住大门时，我们以为自己被困住了。感谢上天，传送门将我们带回了这里。"

#: ../books/il_notes_6.txt:38
msgid ""
"A few of the guys were still working on the floor above and didn't follow us"
" into the chamber. We'll head back down and rendezvous with them tomorrow."
msgstr "几个人还在上面的楼层工作，没有跟我们进入房间。我们明天会回去会合他们。"

#: ../books/il_notes_7.txt:13
msgid "1462/8/13"
msgstr "1462/8/13"

#: ../books/il_notes_7.txt:19
msgid ""
"When we returned today, the layout of the first floor did not match our "
"maps. Thankfully, an Empyrean mage made it back with us. I asked them to try"
" sensing for human life on the lower levels. Zero results thus far, but I "
"still have hope."
msgstr ""
"当我们今天返回时，第一层的布局与我们的地图不符。幸好一位最高天法师带着我们回来了。我请他们尝试感知下层是否有人类生命迹象。到目前为止没有结果，但我仍然抱有希望。"

#: ../books/il_notes_7.txt:38
msgid ""
"The Chamber sees the situation differently. Orders came in for operations to"
" be moved to other nearby sites. Krolan obeyed. Said he didn't want end up "
"dead like \"those guys\". As if our guys are dead! When I find them, we're "
"going to snag the rest of that Mastite for ourselves!"
msgstr ""
"议会对情况有不同的看法。有命令要求将作业转移到其他附近的地点。克罗兰服从了。他说他不想像“那些家伙”一样死。好像我们的家伙已经死了！当我找到他们时，我们将把剩下的魔石抢过来！"

