msgstr "1468/7/9"

#: ../books/wardens_notes.txt:18
msgid ""
"Another subject asked to take the test. I can't remember the last time "
"anyone made it through, but they always want to try. I gave them the same "
"advice as with all the subjects:"
msgstr "又一个考生要求参加考试。我不记得上次有谁通过了，但他们总是想尝试。我给了他们和所有考生一样的建议："

#: ../books/wardens_notes.txt:24
msgid "East at the first symbol."
msgstr "第一个符号向东。"

#: ../books/wardens_notes.txt:29
msgid "South at the next."
msgstr "下一个向南。"

#: ../books/wardens_notes.txt:34
msgid "West two times, then carry on from there."
msgstr "向西两次，然后从那里继续。"

#: ../books/wardens_notes_2.txt:13
msgid ""
"The other subjects had been very eager, so I invited a few to watch today's "
"challenger."
msgstr "其他考生都非常渴望，所以我邀请了几人来观看今天的挑战者。"

#: ../books/wardens_notes_2.txt:18
msgid ""
"The entertainment didn't last long. The subject immediately went south."
msgstr "娱乐没有持续太久。该考生立即向南移动。"

#: ../books/wardens_notes_2.txt:24
msgid "1468/7/10"
msgstr "1468/7/10"

#: ../books/wardens_notes_2.txt:29
