#: ../powers/base/magician/burn.txt:1
msgid "Burn"
msgstr "火龙吐息"

#: ../powers/base/magician/burn.txt:4
msgid ""
"Blast multiple enemies in a distant area with fire. Has a chance to inflict "
"a severe burn that makes enemies very weak to fire damage."
msgstr "用火焰攻击远处的多个敌人。有几率造成严重灼伤，使敌人极度惧怕火焰伤害。"

#: ../powers/base/magician/energy_flow.txt:1
msgid "Energy Flow"
msgstr "能量加成"

#: ../powers/base/magician/energy_flow.txt:2
msgid "Mana reserves are increased and regenerate faster."
msgstr "魔力储备增加，恢复速度加快。"

#: ../powers/base/magician/fireball.txt:1
msgid "Fireball"
msgstr "火球"

#: ../powers/base/magician/fireball.txt:2
msgid "Launch a ball of fire that does extra mental damage."
msgstr "发射一个火球，造成额外的精神伤害。"

#: ../powers/base/magician/thunderstrike.txt:1
msgid "Thunderstrike"
msgstr "电闪雷鸣"

#: ../powers/base/magician/thunderstrike.txt:4
msgid ""
"Lightning strikes from the sky with a high chance to critically damage "
"movement-impaired enemies. Upon striking an enemy, releases a wave of energy"
" that has a chance of stunning other enemies."
msgstr "闪电从天而降，有较高几率对行动受限的敌人造成暴击伤害。击中敌人后，会释放出一道能量波，有几率使其他敌人眩晕。"

#: ../powers/base/magician/shield.txt:4
msgid "Create a force field that absorbs damage."
msgstr "创造一个能吸收伤害的力场。"

#: ../powers/base/magician/shock.txt:1
msgid "Shock"
msgstr "电磁炮"

#: ../powers/base/magician/shock.txt:2
msgid ""
"Shoot a ball of electricity that is extra effective against movement-"
"impaired enemies."
msgstr "发射一个电球，对行动受限的敌人效果更佳。"

#: ../powers/base/magician/mystic_blast.txt:1
msgid "Mystic Blast"
msgstr "神秘冲击"

#: ../powers/base/magician/mystic_blast.txt:2
msgid ""
"Channel an orb that deals dark damage. Targets gain a resistance to dark "
"damage, but become weaker to other types of magic. The effect can be applied"
" up to 3 times on a target."
msgstr "引导一个造成暗属性伤害的光球。目标获得暗属性伤害抗性，但对其他类型魔法的抵抗力降低。该效果最多可对同一目标施加3次。"

#: ../powers/base/magician/ice_bolt.txt:1
msgid "Ice Bolt"
msgstr "冰弹"

#: ../powers/base/magician/ice_bolt.txt:2
msgid "Launch a chunk of ice that slows enemies."
msgstr "发射一块冰块减缓敌人的速度。"

#: ../powers/base/magician/freeze.txt:1
msgid "Freeze"
msgstr "千里冰封"

#: ../powers/base/magician/freeze.txt:4
msgid ""
"Create a ray of several piercing cold shards that slow enemies. Shards have "
"a chance of shattering into a cloud of frost that makes enemies weak to ice "
"damage."
msgstr "释放一道由数道穿透力极强的寒冰碎片组成的光束，减缓敌人的速度。碎片有几率破碎成一团冰霜，使敌人对冰冻伤害变得脆弱。"

#: ../powers/base/magician/summon_skeleton.txt:3
msgid "Summon Skeleton"
msgstr "召唤骷髅"

#: ../powers/base/magician/summon_skeleton.txt:4
msgid ""
"Raise an undead to battle alongside you. Each summoned skeleton reduces your"
" maximum MP."
msgstr "召唤亡灵与你并肩作战。每召唤一个骷髅都会降低你的最大魔法值。"

#: ../powers/base/magician/barrier.txt:1
msgid "Barrier"
msgstr "屏障"

#: ../powers/base/magician/barrier.txt:2
msgid "Applies permanent protection against all elemental damage."
msgstr "提供永久防护，抵御所有元素伤害。"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/quake.txt:1
msgid "Quake"
msgstr "震颤一击"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/quake.txt:4
msgid "Knock back nearby enemies with a chance to stun."
msgstr "击退附近的敌人，并有几率使其眩晕。"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/vampirism.txt:1
msgid "Vampirism"
msgstr "吸血"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/vampirism.txt:4
msgid "Grants attacks the ability to leech enemy health."
msgstr "赋予攻击者吸取敌人生命值的能力。"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/blood_strike.txt:1
msgid "Blood Strike"
msgstr "血刃"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/blood_strike.txt:2
msgid "Deal a powerful blow that inflicts a bleeding wound."
msgstr "给予重击，造成流血伤口。"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/throw_knife.txt:1
msgid "Throw Knife"
msgstr "飞刀"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/throw_knife.txt:2
msgid ""
"Throw a knife to deal reduced melee weapon damage. High accuracy and "
"critical rate."
msgstr "投掷飞刀以造成低于近战武器的伤害。命中率和暴击率高。"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/rupture.txt:1
msgid "Rupture"
msgstr "破裂"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/rupture.txt:4
msgid ""
"Split the ground in a straight line. Enemies caught in the chasm suffer "
"reduced avoidance, absorption, and poise."
msgstr "将地面直线劈开。被困在裂缝中的敌人会降低闪避、吸收和平衡能力。"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/stone_wall.txt:1
msgid "Stone Wall"
msgstr "不倒之躯"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/stone_wall.txt:2
msgid "Withstand stronger attacks with more health and absorption."
msgstr "拥有更高的生命值和吸收能力，可以抵御更强烈的攻击。"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/shield_bash.txt:1
msgid "Shield Bash"
msgstr "势不可当"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/shield_bash.txt:2
msgid "Dash into enemies, crushing them with sheer force."
msgstr "冲向敌人，用强大的力量将他们碾碎。"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/cleave.txt:1
msgid "Cleave"
msgstr "刀光剑影"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/cleave.txt:2
msgid "Attack all enemies in a wide arc."
msgstr "攻击大范围内的所有敌人。"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/throw_axe.txt:1
msgid "Throw Axe"
msgstr "天降巨斧"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/throw_axe.txt:2
msgid "Throw an axe to deal extra melee weapon damage."
msgstr "投掷斧头可以造成额外的近战武器伤害。"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/enchanted_blade.txt:1
msgid "Enchanted Blade"
msgstr "附魔之刃"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/enchanted_blade.txt:2
msgid "Imbues attacks with extra dark damage."
msgstr "使攻击附带额外的暗属性伤害。"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/warcry.txt:1
msgid "Warcry"
msgstr "战吼"

#: ../powers/base/warrior/warcry.txt:4
msgid "Remove debuffs and become immune to debuffs for a limited time."
msgstr "消除负面效果，并在短时间内免疫负面效果。"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/bear_trap.txt:1
msgid "Bear Trap"
msgstr "张机设阱"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/bear_trap.txt:2
msgid ""
"This trap deals extra ranged weapon damage and immobilizes the target. Has a"
" chance to inflict bleeding."
msgstr "此陷阱可造成额外的远程武器伤害并使目标无法移动，有几率造成流血效果。"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/multishot.txt:1
msgid "Multishot"
msgstr "三箭齐发"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/multishot.txt:2
msgid "Shoot multiple projectiles in an arc simultaneously."
msgstr "同时沿弧线发射多个投射物。"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/wolfs_eye.txt:1
msgid "Wolf's Eye"
msgstr "鹰眼"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/wolfs_eye.txt:2
msgid "Improves the ability to hit and critically wound enemies."
msgstr "提高命中和对敌人造成暴击伤害的能力。"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/rapid_fire.txt:1
msgid "Rapid Fire"
msgstr "以攻为防"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/rapid_fire.txt:2
msgid "Fire five low power missiles in quick succession."
msgstr "快速连续发射五枚低阶箭。"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/shoot.txt:1
msgid "Shoot"
msgstr "射箭"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/shoot.txt:4
msgid "Basic ranged attack."
msgstr "基础远程攻击。"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/haste.txt:3
msgid "Move at an increased speed for a limited time."
msgstr "在短时间内以更高的速度移动。"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/poison_shot.txt:1
msgid "Poison Shot"
msgstr "毒箭"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/poison_shot.txt:4
msgid "Shoot a projectile that explodes into a poisonous cloud on impact."
msgstr "发射一枚撞击时会爆炸并产生毒云的投射物。"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/scavenger.txt:1
msgid "Scavenger"
msgstr "拾荒者"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/scavenger.txt:2
msgid ""
"Good fortune shines upon you, revealing treasures that others might have "
"overlooked."
msgstr "好运降临，为你揭示他人可能忽略的宝藏。"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/ember_shot.txt:1
msgid "Ember Shot"
msgstr "火箭"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/ember_shot.txt:2
msgid ""
"Fire a spray of burning embers at close range. Effective against armored "
"enemies. Inflicts a burn that makes enemies weaker to fire damage."
msgstr "近距离喷射燃烧的余烬。对身穿盔甲的敌人有效。造成灼烧效果，使敌人对火焰伤害的抗性降低。"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/charged_shot.txt:1
msgid "Charged Shot"
msgstr "蓄力射击"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/charged_shot.txt:2
msgid "Draw a shot for an extended period, increasing its impact."
msgstr "延长射击时间，增强其冲击力。"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/caltrops.txt:1
msgid "Caltrops"
msgstr "暗器"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/caltrops.txt:2
msgid ""
"This trap deals reduced ranged weapon damage and slows the target. Can "
"affect multiple targets."
msgstr "此陷阱会降低远程武器伤害并减缓目标速度，可影响多个目标。"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/piercing_shot.txt:1
msgid "Piercing Shot"
msgstr "一箭双雕"

#: ../powers/base/ranger/piercing_shot.txt:2
msgid "Fire a shot that ignores armor and goes through multiple enemies."
